      "content": "really? i was reading online that a little bit of alcohol actually makes sedatives work better because they both hit the same receptors. like, wouldn't the wine just help the zolpidem do its job faster since i'm already a bit relaxed? i only had one glass so it's not like i'm drunk or anything.",
